        <div n="Z707V82-" type="poem"><head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-Z707V82--headnote-1"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-Z707V82--headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-Z707V82--headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head><head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-Z707V82--headnote-2"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-Z707V82--headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-Z707V82--headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head><head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-Z707V82--headnote-3"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-Z707V82--headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-Z707V82--headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head>
      <lg n="1" type="triplet"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-Z707V82--line-1"><hi rend="display-initial">U</hi>Nto Prelatick Order you'd ascend</l><l n="2" xml:id="spp-Z707V82--line-2"> Come on, I'll shew you how to do't, My Friend,</l><l n="3" xml:id="spp-Z707V82--line-3"> Do not in Study waste the precious Day,</l><l n="4" xml:id="spp-Z707V82--line-4"> To <hi rend="underline">Necessary</hi> Knowledge short's the Way,</l><l n="5" xml:id="spp-Z707V82--line-5"> Turn over a few Books, and learn to prate,</l><l n="6" xml:id="spp-Z707V82--line-6"> Leave others solidly Things to debate.</l><l n="7" xml:id="spp-Z707V82--line-7"> Load not with serious Piety your Breast,</l><l n="8" xml:id="spp-Z707V82--line-8"> Alas! at COURT 'tis nothing but a Jest;</l><l n="9" xml:id="spp-Z707V82--line-9"> Yet let a feigned Gravity take Place,</l><l n="10" xml:id="spp-Z707V82--line-10"> And Complaisance still dwell upon your Face.</l><l n="11" xml:id="spp-Z707V82--line-11"> Within your Parish never should you stay,</l><l n="12" xml:id="spp-Z707V82--line-12"> Nor to your People Preach or with them Pray,</l><l n="13" xml:id="spp-Z707V82--line-13"> Your <hi rend="underline">Constant Business</hi> lyes another Way.</l><l n="14" xml:id="spp-Z707V82--line-14"> To please great Men must your chief Study be,</l><l n="15" xml:id="spp-Z707V82--line-15"> And win the Ladies too with----- Pleasantry.</l><l n="16" xml:id="spp-Z707V82--line-16"> Follow these Rules with Care, if you be wise,</l><l n="17" xml:id="spp-Z707V82--line-17"> Experience shews 'tis the best Way to rise.</l></lg></div>
      </div>
